  "body": "In order to implement this we will need to \r\n- Compute the total deposits of every validator who participated in the last epoch \r\n- Compute the online reward and offline penalty based on Casper FFG Incentive(not specified yet)\r\n- Add the online reward to every validator that participated in the last epoch and subtract the penalty from those who did not\r\n\r\nRewards for crosslinks are not in scope for Ruby so will be pushed to the next release.\r\nAlso slashing conditions , ex: penalties for signing or attesting to non-canonical-chain blocks ,etc have not been fully specified yet. so we can stub them out until it gets elaborated on in the research spec",
